content: Had some difficulty getting the app to work initially. However, after assistance from the company, managed to get it to work perfectly. Very impressive app which allows you to display your photos on your watch.

Easy to use & as expected! But there are two things that needs to be improved: Currently, the quality of the displayed image is lowered, compared to the default watch face (My Photo+) on my Samsung Galaxy Watch, tested with same photo. Lastly, this app needs more customization options (i.e. Custom time/date positioning, more fonts options, more time/date style, etc.)
